{
  "stem": "1753.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 95.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What you were talking about before you put that new cartridge in here is I believe I indicated that I wasn't that-- wood-- in the area where they're stored, that lumber--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--shed.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said to myself, now how am I going to get out from here?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew the area like my pocket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew where shovels were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew where pickaxes were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somehow I made my-- got out from under this lumber.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was careful and I watched the guards, and I timed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were crossing each other about every 10 minutes or 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Besides the guard that was on the tower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I walked over about six, eight, 10 yards to the left, and there was a [? field ?] shovel, one of those collapsible ones.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I could see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was dark but not pitch dark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I could see in all the good sense, and I could feel and I knew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's because I've been in the area many, many times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I got myself a pick axe and one of those little shovels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as soon as the guards crossed each other and went in the opposite direction, I went to the first fence, which wouldn't be further away than 10 yards from the edge of that shed.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And I took that hand shovel in there, and I was absolutely amazed the ground was so terribly soft that it took me less than a minute to dig a little hole, a little area, that would allow me to crawl under that first set of barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And even there, I just needed to lift it 10 inches, move it up and crawl underneath.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
